  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b86\u0baf\u0bc1\u0ba4 \u0baa\u0bb2\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b8a\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd - \u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Relive the history of dictators who tried to stifle democracy through force of arms - The Dulles Report",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "This government must revisit the history of the lessons taught by the people to dictatorial rulers who try to stifle democracy and freedom of the people through force of arms. Member of Parliament Dallas Alagaperuma said that all the opposition parties will unite and raise their voice against such repressions as an all-party unity.",
        "He said this while addressing a joint press conference with the participation of members of the opposition parties on the theme of \"All Party Unity\" at the Office of the Leader of the Opposition in Colombo.",
        "The government imposed a state of emergency and the attack on empty-faced protesters was the first step in anti-democratic activities.",
        "These attacks on demonstrators today will no doubt flow on trade unionists tomorrow. It then flows over the media. Similarly, the government will take action against other political parties.",
        "So if you don't speak out against this oppression today, no one will come forward to speak out against you tomorrow.",
        "Both security and freedom of the country are to be protected at the same time. But curtailing people's freedom on the pretext of security is unacceptable.",
        "We urge the government to look back at the history of how the people have taught a lesson in the end times to dictatorial rulers who try to stifle people's democracy and freedom through force of arms.",
        "This is the occasion when this country fights for independence. All the people are looking forward to a peaceful country moving forward. He said that as an all-party unity, all the opposition parties have come together to emphasize that we can never allow anything contrary to that."
      ],
